org.springframework.aop.framework.adapter

类 AfterReturningAdviceInterceptor

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.springframework.aop.framework.adapter.AfterReturningAdviceInterceptor
  • 所有已实现的接口:
    java.io.Serializable, Advice, Interceptor, MethodInterceptor, AfterAdvice

    public class AfterReturningAdviceInterceptor
extends java.lang.Object
implements MethodInterceptor, AfterAdvice, java.io.Serializable
    Interceptor to wrap an AfterReturningAdvice. Used internally by the AOP framework; application developers should not need to use this class directly.
    作者:
    Rod Johnson
    另请参阅:
    MethodBeforeAdviceInterceptor, ThrowsAdviceInterceptor, 序列化表格

    • 方法详细资料

      • invoke

        public java.lang.Object invoke(MethodInvocation mi)
                        throws java.lang.Throwable
        从接口复制的说明: MethodInterceptor
        Implement this method to perform extra treatments before and after the invocation. Polite implementations would certainly like to invoke Joinpoint.proceed().
        指定者:
        invoke 在接口中 MethodInterceptor
        参数:
        mi - the method invocation joinpoint
        返回:
        the result of the call to Joinpoint.proceed(); might be intercepted by the interceptor
        抛出:
        java.lang.Throwable - if the interceptors or the target object throws an exception
